<title>超3.2万家企业，携百万件新品奔赴这场盛会！</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E5%8D%97%E9%83%BD%E5%91%A8%E5%88%8A+%E8%B6%853.2%E4%B8%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%90%BA%E7%99%BE%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81%E5%A5%94%E8%B5%B4%E8%BF%99%E5%9C%BA%E7%9B%9B%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%81</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_content&quot; id=&quot;js_content&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;图片&quot; class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V9V83VFzia0RxiaK3eOWibdaTQbp9fz5bxLDOr9LRl0nibN9wB40ATibG6h7ibntXCn3U5UfmdF9BNYJX3ECFf8QLgUg/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;amp;from=appmsg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;图片&quot; class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V9V83VFzia0TzpazRHiaUD7qgPRVzxlbeibBdAHnT67xfibKV4l0BOR747iaKqLa4zKnLI8Vp7ymUUGm2onwZV7xiaWA/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;本文自南都·湾财社。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;摄影报道&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt; | &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;南都N视频记者 冯宙锋&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;视频| &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;南都·湾财社记者 邱康正 叶浩程 杨文瑾&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;编辑 | 柴华&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;channels_iframe_wrp&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;&gt;10月15日，第138届广交会在广州开幕。本届广交会参展企业数量、展位数量均创下历史新高，超3.2万家企业携百万件新品奔赴这场外贸盛会，向世界集中展示中国制造的“向新”与“向智”的活力。开展第一天，现场情况如何？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHn8YIFSVuiaFb8zo6fuIz6vZiaL62MkTmaH7XsxicZHnaib5otlfMibqybLfg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHn7pag1WpsTK7sTVRKmmibQKY4ILlEnQcmZd3leWUTVUD6Syka2MR3a4Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHn0eK7QdSDKZTdL24J0sPuwbgLOIY0Z5zkibWeic8kvvNFkjfv4SIaKlEg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHngxAyaYr0VicXdsCviaYGJKYESOx8l914b4E75Q8FXrvm47aYSCFzxSMg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;&gt;第138届广交会依然是分三期举办，每期的展览时间为五天。第一期展览的主题是先进制造，包括像电子家电、工业装备等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHnpaQkVkxbeAJvDBUUAus408CgpiaDia8C0IYL2JvClmOhmK5XfGHvEmEA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHnAOjmLapmiaTiaIU0NFcfnKxBKfN8ibWnGYibiaNhbpRicuxppJAqNVo3LEfg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHntosLlIUKQr9UmAhOCATNs4xuZ1CsUicHpy28aqY3icuAqicsvgPWb03icQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;&gt;数据显示，本届展会已吸引超24万名采购商预登记，其中，来自欧盟、美国、“一带一路”共建国家的采购商增长幅度最为明显。同时，在参展企业方面也有不少新变化，首先是展位数量和参展企业都创下新高，在3.2万家参展企业中有大约3600家是首次参展；而且优质企业数量也更多，拥有高新技术、专精特新、单项冠军等称号的企业总数首次超过了1万家，占企业总数的三成以上。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHnQgMsSyViaJwmuHGvy6CxpOnBxoEx8fKEYGaBmH02jbTgic041ghA50Xg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHn2Orbh1U6aDBsheiaU2Iv1GeGDkptCicwzdmZXOwibsuPGplqBuWGfrptQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHnLk3YKIjvI5gWjm0QsDNMNv6AGnypuIRzgvLO2gt5KKKygDRuUxYOjA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/V9V83VFzia0TGpibfnoGicB6vxgicBKI7wHnich2SicKmibZAW7Cd8jNxkpiaLo11xdCpgHEYlp4Ndks6IWX4rNTgaFbrQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;from=appmsg&quot; type=&quot;block&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;END&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;mp_profile_iframe_wrp&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;图片&quot; class=&quot;rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/V9V83VFzia0QoMAF1picfl3Dx0L3tDgDUOEKVsplMv3ibS0UdicD7qufPp4MMOjaePPiaT5Ex8o6YZnUuxchf5XAiaug/640?wx_fmt=gif#imgIndex=5&quot; /&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;display: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    

    
